## ✨ Key Features
- **Persona-Driven Navigation:** A custom interface that pivots data and storytelling based on the viewer (Retailer, Sponsor, or Promoter).
- **Cinematic Hero:** High-fidelity video background with optimized delivery for Safari and mobile devices.
- **Glassmorphism UI:** A luxury-brand aesthetic inspired by Apple and Tesla.
- **Data-Driven Storytelling:** Interactive "By The Numbers" module with count-up animations to show market dominance.

## 🤖 AI Integration & Fluency
This project was built using an "AI-First" workflow to maximize speed and craft:
- **Cursor AI:** Used for rapid prototyping and complex Framer Motion logic.
- **Midjourney/Generative AI:** Created high-end luxury retail renderings to supplement official media assets.
- **LLM Prompt Engineering:** Leveraged AI to refine the sales narrative and ensure a "luxury brand" tone throughout the copy.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 14 (App Router)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS (Custom Glassmorphism configuration)
- **Animations:** Framer Motion (Scroll-triggered and state-based transitions)
- **Deployment:** Vercel

